                "html": "<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">一、分管领导</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">次日上午，八点钟左右，我从宿舍里洗漱完了之后到早餐点过早。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">走路到聂哥昨日带我看过的早餐点后，看着墙上的价格，一瞬间我竟有种错觉。心里暗想“在学校了热干面只要四块钱，再不济在宜昌外面餐馆，一碗热干面也只要五块钱吧，这里竟然要六块？”于是点了份最便宜的素面。“叮，支付宝到帐5元”。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">回到办公室里，先是提着开水瓶到净水器饮水机那里去打水。打完水之后，张主任也来办公室了，过了一会儿之后，聂哥也来了。我坐在办公桌前，拿着一本《中国共产党简史》读得摇头晃脑,并试着用方言读出来，入乡随俗（结果最后也没学会，不过听倒是不成问题）。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“义波，新来的同志呢？”人未至声音已经先到我们办公室了。我见对面的聂哥站了起来，立马也紧张地站了起来。“黄书记好！”聂哥说道。“黄书记？不是黄主任吗？”我心里暗想。张主任也从里面办公室走了出来，顺势说道“这个就是新来的三支一扶的同志，叫xxx,是三峡大学毕业的；昨天下午刚到，住宿都安排好了。”黄书记立马问道“住在哪里啊？条件怎么样？还适应嘛？”不等张主任回答，我立马说“还可以吧，房间小了点，不过男生没问题。”张主任也即使补充道“现在政府没有宿舍了，先暂住在那里吧，等后面有其他宿舍空出来了再搬。”“好吧！那你暂时先带他熟悉熟悉工作，聂xx也把相关工作教一下，争取早点学会。”黄书记说着边走出了办公室的门。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“聂哥，刚刚那个是谁啊？”黄书记走了之后我立马悄悄问道。“是我们的分管领导，乡党委副书记、副乡长，分管农业和乡村振兴的。”聂哥也接着回复我，然后又说道：“其他人的话你可以不听，但是黄书记的工作安排你一定要听，她是负责分管你的所有工作的，到时候考核什么的都要她签字。”“哦，哦，哦”我若有所思地点了点头。紧接着聂哥又开始忙着他自己的事情去了。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">二、造假</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“聂哥，你要不安排点事情给我搞吧，我这一上午啥也没干。”看了一上午书的我顿感有些愧疚，于是朝聂哥问道。聂哥抬了抬头，说道“现在也没什么事情，你要不把这个雨露计划的资料再审一审吧，看有没有差的，差的话还要联系村里要。”“好的好的！”我立马拿起了2021年秋季和2022年春季雨露计划的两个文件夹，坐会到了自己的座位上，按照花名册的顺序一个个审核起资料起来。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“聂哥，聂哥，你看这个人的学籍资料，像不像是p的，我对比了一下她两年的学籍资料签字，好像都是一模一样的。”我从高高的档案盒中抬起头来，立马向聂哥说道。聂哥一听也急忙从他的位子上跑到了我座位这一边来，拿起我手上的两套学籍资料，“我靠，这个老6！”聂哥忍不住地爆粗口。我补充到：“可能是因为一般的学校都是3年制，我看她这写的2.5年制，所以才搞错了吧。”</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">说着聂哥拿起了电话，“喂，郑x，你们村有个叫xxx的学生，她的在校学籍资料是p的，你有没有她的联系方式啊。”电话那头也传来了惊讶的语气，“啊，这孩子怎么干这种事情呢？我赶紧和她联系一下，核实一下情况。”</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">稍过一会儿，电话来了。电话那头说道：“是的，是的，这孩子去年就毕业了，现在在工作着呢。那现在这个钱发出去了要怎么收回呢？”“我先问问吧。”说着聂哥又拿起了手机，同县里的相关负责人沟通了起来。“是的，是的，我们这新来的同事检查资料看出来一个学生的学籍资料是P的。”“已经和学生本人联系了，同意退款，这个钱要怎么操作？”聂哥向电话那头的人问道。“哦，哦，打到国库是吧，好的，等会您把国库的收款码发给我，我联系学生去打。”说完聂哥也挂掉了电话。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">午饭时间，聂哥与其它同事一桌，我坐在旁边桌上，隐隐约约听到聂哥说道：“我们新来的同事，上午看资料看出来一个学籍资料p是P图的老6。”“还不错！”我心里暗暗想到。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">用了一天多的时间，将所有的资料对着花名册看了一遍又一遍，多的拿出来，缺的联系村里发电子档过来，然后打印出来，终于整整齐齐，完完整整地将所有资料都整好了。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">三、走访入户</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">接下来的一个早晨，“张主任，有没有什么稿子写的，我想锻炼一下我的写作能力。”我走到张主任办公桌前问道，心里则暗暗的想：“借写稿子锻炼一下自己的申论写作能力，应该挺好的吧，今年国考申论一塌糊涂。”张主任立马坐直了身子，然后又立马靠在了椅子上，思索了片刻，说道：“我这有篇稿子，是关于树立典型的，你拿去看看吧。然后写一篇推荐材料。”“好的，好的！”我立马兴奋地搓起了手，然后回到了办公桌上，打开了电脑，登录qq,看着张主任发过来的电子档文件，精准地点击了“接受”。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">“小拳头托起大世界”看着这个题目，我的内心满是震撼，对于一个申论的菜鸡来说，光看到这个题目我就知道，我写不出来这个稿子。于是我接着一句又一句地看了下去。对仗工整，排比恰当，真材实例句句不谈伟大，字里行间，却让我真心佩服这个素未谋面的陌生人。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">下午，当我还在抓耳挠腮，埋头苦钻地在想如何遣词用句时，张主任提着包，走过来说道“xx，跟我一起下队去一趟。”我立马从写作的阴影中走出来，抬头回复到“好的！”聂哥瞧我刚来没有公文包，于是站起来，从柜子里翻出来一个皮包，我将笔记本和水杯都装进去，跟着张主任一起下了楼。</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">车上，“张主任，我们这是去干什么嘛？”我摇晃着询问到；张主任说“等会你就知道了。”车子拐过一个又一个的弯道，我从窗外看去，漫山绿色的柑橘树中夹着点点黄斑，那是成熟的九月红（一种柑橘品种）。我不禁想到“若不是这漫山的柑橘树，这里的老百姓们该怎么生活啊？”</p> \n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: